 Legion Partners: Don’t Be Misled By RCM Technologies Management, Warns Largest Stockholder 
         










    










 






 











 









Legion Partners: Don't Be Misled By RCM Technologies Management, Warns Largest Stockholder

		  LEGION PARTNERS CALLS ON STOCKHOLDERS TO STOP "FREE FALL," VOTE FOR REAL CHANGE WITH NEW HIGHLY QUALIFIED DIRECTOR NOMINEES ON GOLD PROXY CARD
		

Oct 31, 2013, 13:31 ET
		  		  					
						 from   Legion Partners Asset Management, LLC 











 
















































 

 






















































 























 























 

 

 
 
 
 







