Company Overview of Legion Partners, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Legion Partners, LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to institutional and high net worth clients. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The firm seeks to invest in value stocks of small and micro-cap companies. Legion Partners, LLC is based in Los Angeles, California.


